    dcterms:description "15 wt% NiO on CeO2 support, calcined at 500 deg C",
        "15 wt% NiO on CeO2 support, co-precipitated at pH 8.5, calcined 500 deg C / 4 h, active phase Ni0 formed by in situ reduction",
        "15 wt% NiO on CeO2 support, co-precipitated at pH 8.5, calcined 500 deg C / 4 h, sieved to 250-500 um",
        "15 wt% NiO on CeO2, calcined at 500 deg C / 4 h" ;
    dcterms:title "NiO/CeO2 dry reforming catalyst",
        "NiO/CeO2 dry reforming catalyst (calcined precursor)",
        "NiO/CeO2 dry reforming catalyst (calcined)" .

